      <item>
        <title>VirtualBox SMBus error</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;VirtualBox4.36安装Ubuntu13.10报&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;ruby&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;piix4_smbus&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mo&quot;&gt;0000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mo&quot;&gt;00&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mo&quot;&gt;07&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;SMBus&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;base&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;address&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;uninitialized&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;err&quot;&gt;–&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;upgrade&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;bios&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ow&quot;&gt;or&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;use&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;force_addr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mh&quot;&gt;0xadd&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;r&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;解决办法：
add “blacklist i2c_piix4” to file
/etc/modprobe.d/modprobe.conf&lt;/p&gt;

